  "title": "PRIME MOVER DRIVERS",
  "description": "<p><strong>We’re looking for committed and responsible Class 3 / 3A licensed drivers to join our team in operating Prime Movers for container and cargo transport.</strong><br /></p><p><u><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></u></p><p>•Operate a Prime Mover for transporting containers and general cargo within port areas or designated zones</p><p>•Ensure safe and timely loading/unloading and delivery</p><p>•Follow safety protocols and SOPs at all times</p><p>•Maintain vehicle cleanliness and report any issues</p><p><u><strong>Work Schedule Options:</strong></u></p><p>Fixed Monthly Days: Minimum<u> 22 or 25 </u>working days</p><p>Work Pattern: 4 days work, 2 days off</p><p>Rotating Shifts:</p><p>•<strong>Day </strong>Shift: 7:30 AM – 7:30 PM</p><p>•<strong>Night </strong>Shift: 7:30 PM – 7:30 AM</p><p>Work Pattern: 4 days work, 2 days off</p><p>What's in it for You?</p><p>•Full Training Provided – If you're new to prime mover operations</p><p>•CPF, Medical & Other Benefits Included</p><p>•Joining Bonus Up To<strong> $16,000!</strong> (T&C APPLIES)</p><p>•Attractive incentive;</p><p><u><em>✔️Weekend incentives ✔️Night shift incentives ✔️Transport allowance ✔️Performance & safety incentives ✔️Box commission</em></u></p><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><p>•No experience needed <u><strong>(training provided!)</strong></u></p><p>•Able to work at heights is a plus</p><p>•Willing to work on rotating shift and outdoors</p>",
